@startuml
title Top10 Mapping Reporter - Use Cases (v0.1)

left to right direction

actor "User\n(Analyst)" as U

rectangle "Top10 Mapping Reporter" as SYS {
  usecase "Enter target URL" as UC1
  usecase "Run checks" as UC2
  usecase "View results\n(by OWASP category)" as UC3
  usecase "Download report\n(HTML/MD)" as UC4
  usecase "Save evidence files\n(runs/<id>)" as UC5
}

U --> UC1
U --> UC2
U --> UC3
U --> UC4

UC2 ..> UC5 : <<include>>
UC2 ..> UC3 : <<include>>

note right of SYS
No login/session flows in MVP.
HTTP response-based checks only.
end note

@enduml